00:12:31.390 --> 00:12:32.460
Apa bunyi bising itu?

00:12:34.430 --> 00:12:37.160
- Jangan tolak saya! - Apa yang mereka katakan?

00:12:38.030 --> 00:12:39.600
Saya akan kembali segera.

00:12:45.940 --> 00:12:47.870
Baiklah, mari fokus.

00:12:48.570 --> 00:12:52.310
ya. Juga, Very Berry melangkaui analisis mudah angka.

00:12:52.380 --> 00:12:55.950
Ia menganalisis calon dan parti. Sejurus selepas dasar diumumkan...

00:12:56.010 --> 00:12:58.050
kita boleh mengukur perubahan pendapat umum.

00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:00.820
Ya, Profesor Eum Nan Sae.

00:13:01.190 --> 00:13:04.220
Jadi anda mengatakan ia menganalisis perkara selain orang?

